00:00:56.600 --> 00:01:55.600
Bonus Fact #1: Use your hard-earned gems only on rewards that *guarantee* you five-star cards. Your first altar draw, then the gold chests in the mazes are good ways to build a strong deck.

00:02:19.300 --> 00:03:12.600
Bonus Fact #2: While duplicate cards all have the same base skills, you can personalize your deck with the Enhancement feature that lets you add one extra skill of your choice.

00:03:30.600 --> 00:05:06.200
Bonus Fact #3: Each level in the campaign map has "shards" of a certain card. Using the Explore feature, you can gather these shards to build the deck you want over time.

